---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Curriculum from "../assets/Fabian_CV_2.pdf"
import 'animate.css';
---

<Layout title="Portfolio Fabian Casas">
  <section class="mt-[4rem] md:mt-[4rem] 2xl:mt-[8rem] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center p-1">
      <h1 data-cursor="text"  class="  transition-colors duration-300 ease-in-out animate__animated animate__fadeInDown animate__slow tracking-tight leading-tight w-full lg:w-8/12 2xl:w-7/12 text-black dark:text-white">
        ¡Hola! Soy <span  
        >Fabián Casas</span> <span   class="transparent">Front&minus;End</span> Devoloper
      </h1>
      <p
      data-cursor="text" 
        class="transition-colors duration-300 ease-in-out animate__animated animate__fadeInUp animate__slow w-11/12 text-sm md:text-base lg:w-8/12 xl:w-6/12 my-5 text-black dark:text-stone-400"
      >
        Estudiante de la carrera Analista Programador en Duoc UC y me encuentro
        en busca de mi práctica profesional, me he desempeñado en Frontend
        (JavaScript, Angular, Astro, Bootstrap) y algo de Backend (Django,
        FireBase, SQL, MySQL).
      </p>
      
      <div class=" mt-5 flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-5">
        <a
          href="/proyectos"
          class="animate__animated animate__fadeInLeft animate__slow relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 py-3 overflow-hidden text-lg font-medium  border-2 dark:border-white border-black   rounded-full hover:text-white group"
        >
          <span
            class="absolute left-0 block w-full h-0 transition-all backdrop-blur-xl bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/10  opacity-100 group-hover:h-full top-1/2 group-hover:top-0 duration-400 ease"
          ></span>
          <span
            class="absolute right-0 flex items-center justify-start w-10 h-10 duration-300 transform translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 ease"
          >
            <svg
              class="w-5 h-5 text-black dark:text-white"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              ><path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                stroke-width="2"
                d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          <span class="relative text-black dark:text-white">Proyectos</span>
        </a>


        <a
          href={Curriculum}
          target="_blank"
          class=" animate__animated animate__fadeInRight animate__slow relative inline-flex items-center justify-center px-12 py-3 overflow-hidden text-lg font-medium  border-2 rounded-full dark:border-white border-black hover:text-white group"
        >
          <span
            class="absolute left-0 block w-full h-0 transition-all bg-black/5 dark:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl  opacity-100 group-hover:h-full top-1/2 group-hover:top-0 duration-400 ease"
          ></span>
          <span
            class="absolute right-0 flex items-center justify-start w-10 h-10 duration-300 transform translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0 ease"
          >
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              width="24"
              height="24"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="2"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              class="icon icon-tabler text-black dark:text-white icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-download"
              ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path><path
                d="M4 17v2a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2 -2v-2"></path><path
                d="M7 11l5 5l5 -5"></path><path d="M12 4l0 12"></path></svg
            >
          </span>
          <span class="relative text-black dark:text-white">Descargar CV</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style scoped>
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(45px, 8vw, 72px);
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .transparent{
    color: transparent; /* El fondo de las letras es transparente */

    text-stroke: 2px black; /* Para otros navegadores compatibles */
  }
</style>
